[{"title":"人是否会因为知道的太多而烦恼","date":"2019-03-22T04:42:46.000Z","path":"2019/03/2019-03-22-zddtd/","content":"<p>​    以前的我会执着的认为，人不应该因为自己知道的太多而烦恼，现在的我认为，这是一种固执的想法。每个人的精力是有限的，当我们掌握了过多的正面或负面的信息之后，并不一定能对我们的判断有更好的促进，更多的信息意味着我们很可能会迷失在对细节的追逐，而这往往会影响我们做出最贴近直觉的判断。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>","excerpt":"​ 以前的我会执着的认为，人不应该因为自己知道的太多而烦恼，现在的我认为，这是一种固执的想法。每个人的精力是有限的，当我们掌握了过多的正面或负面的信息之后，并不一定能对我们的判断有更好的促进，更多的信息意味着我们很可能会迷失在对细节的追逐，而这往往会影响我们做出最贴近直觉的判断。","categories":[{"name":"所思所想","slug":"所思所想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/所思所想/"}],"tags":[{"name":"瞎想","slug":"瞎想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/瞎想/"}]},{"title":"日常生活营养食谱（不定期更新）","date":"2018-04-13T09:32:07.000Z","path":"2018/04/2018-04-13-YYSP/","content":"<p>每天的家庭生活都是要重复做很多菜，这里做个记录，以便不断优化菜品。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"下饭菜\"><a href=\"#下饭菜\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下饭菜\"></a>下饭菜</h2><h3 id=\"酸辣土豆丝\"><a href=\"#酸辣土豆丝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"酸辣土豆丝\"></a>酸辣土豆丝</h3><ul>\n<li><p>食材：</p>\n<p>土豆2个，蒜瓣2瓣、小葱3根，小红椒2根、食盐、生抽</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>步骤：</p>\n<p>土豆削皮擦丝儿，用清水淘三遍去淀粉防粘锅（<strong>这一步不能忘</strong>），泡上水；蒜2瓣切末，小葱三根切碎，2根小红椒切碎，锅放油，把土豆丝水倒出，等烧热微微冒烟，下蒜末，倒土豆丝，翻炒，下小红椒碎末。放生抽，食盐，葱花，出锅。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"西红柿炒蛋\"><a href=\"#西红柿炒蛋\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"西红柿炒蛋\"></a>西红柿炒蛋</h3><ul>\n<li>有空再说</li>\n</ul>\n<p>酸辣白菜</p>\n<p>青椒炒肉</p>\n<p>韭菜苔炒蛋</p>\n<p>秋葵炒鸡蛋</p>\n<p>可乐鸡翅</p>\n<p>辣子鸡/鸭</p>\n<p>红烧茄子</p>\n<p>辣炒花蛤</p>\n<p>黄焖鸡 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>红烧鱼</p>\n<p>肉末豆角</p>\n<p>宫保鸡丁 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>孜然牛肉土豆片 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>手撕包菜 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>干锅菜花 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<h2 id=\"凉菜\"><a href=\"#凉菜\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"凉菜\"></a>凉菜</h2><p>凉拌黄瓜</p>\n<p>凉拌海带丝</p>\n<p>凉拌木耳</p>\n<h2 id=\"煲汤\"><a href=\"#煲汤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"煲汤\"></a>煲汤</h2><p>鱼头汤/鲫鱼汤</p>\n<p>小鸡炖蘑菇</p>\n<p>冬瓜排骨汤</p>\n<p>[紫菜]西红柿蛋汤</p>\n<h2 id=\"面食\"><a href=\"#面食\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"面食\"></a>面食</h2><h3 id=\"焖面\"><a href=\"#焖面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"焖面\"></a>焖面</h3><ul>\n<li>这个会，有空写</li>\n</ul>\n<p>番茄鸡蛋面</p>\n","excerpt":"每天的家庭生活都是要重复做很多菜，这里做个记录，以便不断优化菜品。","categories":[{"name":"日常生活","slug":"日常生活","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/日常生活/"}],"tags":[{"name":"生活","slug":"生活","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/生活/"}]},{"title":"思维反射&肌肉反射","date":"2018-04-11T05:25:56.000Z","path":"2018/04/思维反射/","content":"<p>将学习过程和能力形成的过程进行分析，在进行新技能的认知过程中，我们可以有迹可循，从而通过形成快速认知习惯加快认知过程本身。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>我们不断的学习, 目标可以分为三个阶段：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>进行长久的记忆存储</li>\n<li>讲这些记忆进行关联</li>\n<li>将这些新的关联体进行再次存储</li>\n</ol>\n<p>步骤2可以帮我们理解认知我们学接触到的信息，步骤3是推动这个世界的源力，我们的知识正是千百年来一代一代的人的结晶，通过各种形式把步骤3形成的新关联体以各种形式记录下来。所以我们都是站在巨人的肩膀上。</p>\n<p>社交天才和运动天才在抽象层面上说，其机理几乎如出一辙：一个是思维记忆，另一个是肌肉记忆。前者可以让我们思考更迅速、全面，或者可以让我们反应更灵敏、有节奏感。</p>\n","excerpt":"将学习过程和能力形成的过程进行分析，在进行新技能的认知过程中，我们可以有迹可循，从而通过形成快速认知习惯加快认知过程本身。","categories":[{"name":"所思所想","slug":"所思所想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/所思所想/"}],"tags":[{"name":"瞎想","slug":"瞎想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/瞎想/"}]},{"title":"ReactJS - day01 入门知识","date":"2018-04-10T17:14:08.000Z","path":"2018/04/ReactJS-day01/","content":"<p>介绍React开发环境的初始化，主要包括：组件定义、props属性、state状态、组件生命周期、事件处理</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"React环境初始化\"><a href=\"#React环境初始化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"React环境初始化\"></a>React环境初始化</h2><h3 id=\"入门介绍\"><a href=\"#入门介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"入门介绍:\"></a>入门介绍:</h3><blockquote>\n<p>声明式：数据驱动</p>\n<p>组件化：把相似的代码放到一起进行复用，传递数据</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><h4 id=\"官网\"><a href=\"#官网\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"官网:\"></a>官网:</h4></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>英文:<a href=\"https://reactjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">https://reactjs.org/</a></p>\n<p>中文:<a href=\"https://doc.react-china.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">https://doc.react-china.org/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"方式一-脚手架-快捷、稳定\"><a href=\"#方式一-脚手架-快捷、稳定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方式一: 脚手架 (快捷、稳定)\"></a>方式一: 脚手架 (快捷、稳定)</h3><ul>\n<li>官方教程: <a href=\"https://doc.react-china.org/docs/add-react-to-a-new-app.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">参考链接1</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app#create-react-app-\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">参考链接2</a></li>\n<li><p>执行命令:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g create-react-app</span><br><span class=\"line\">create-react-app my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm start</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 或使用以下命令 If you have npm 5.2.0+ installed, you may use npx instead.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npx create-react-app my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"方式二-Webpack-步骤较多按下不表\"><a href=\"#方式二-Webpack-步骤较多按下不表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方式二:  Webpack (步骤较多按下不表)\"></a>方式二:  Webpack (步骤较多按下不表)</h3><h2 id=\"元素渲染\"><a href=\"#元素渲染\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"元素渲染\"></a>元素渲染</h2><p>元素是构成 React 应用的最小单位。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> element = &lt;h1&gt;Hello, world&lt;/h1&gt;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>渲染元素</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'react'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'react-dom'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> element = &lt;h1&gt;Hello, world&lt;/h1&gt;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">  element,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"string\">'root'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>React和ReactDOM为以下入口文件代码默认导包</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"组件及组件状态\"><a href=\"#组件及组件状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件及组件状态\"></a>组件及组件状态</h2><p>组件可以将界面分割成一些的独立的、可复用的组成部分，我们只需专注于构建每一个单独的部分。按钮，对话框，列表，输入框都是组件。</p>\n<p>组件从概念上看就像是函数，它可以接收任意的输入值（称之为“props”），并返回一个需要在页面上展示的React元素。</p>\n<h3 id=\"函数定义组件-无状态\"><a href=\"#函数定义组件-无状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数定义组件(无状态)\"></a>函数定义组件(无状态)</h3><p>JavaScript函数</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">Hello</span>(<span class=\"params\">props</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> &lt;h1&gt;Hi, &#123;props.name&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"类定义组件-有状态\"><a href=\"#类定义组件-有状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"类定义组件(有状态)\"></a>类定义组件(有状态)</h3><p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">class由es6支持</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Hello</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">React</span>.<span class=\"title\">Component</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> &lt;h1&gt;Hi, &#123;this.props.name&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>以上两个组件效果在React中相同</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注意： <strong>组件名首字母必须大写</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"组合组件\"><a href=\"#组合组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组合组件\"></a>组合组件</h3><p>组件之间可以相互引用, 通常把App组件作为根组件。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">App</span>(<span class=\"params\">props</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;h1&gt;&#123;props.team&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;p&gt;成立时间: &#123;props.date.toLocaleString()&#125;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;p&gt;成员&#123;props.count&#125;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"悟空\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"三藏\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"八戒\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"沙僧\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    );</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;App team=\"西天取经团\" date=&#123;new Date()&#125; count=&#123;4&#125;/&gt;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    document.getElementById('root')</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>可在Chrome安装React插件查看结构</p>\n<p>注意：<strong>组件的返回值只能有一个根元素, 所以用一个div包裹所有Hello元素</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Props-属性\"><a href=\"#Props-属性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Props 属性\"></a>Props 属性</h3><blockquote>\n<p>props有两种输入方式：<strong>字符串“”</strong> ， <strong>大括号{}</strong></p>\n<p>props不可修改，<strong>属性只读</strong>， 强行修改会报错</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"State-状态\"><a href=\"#State-状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"State 状态\"></a>State 状态</h3><h4 id=\"自动更新时钟\"><a href=\"#自动更新时钟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自动更新时钟\"></a>自动更新时钟</h4><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">tick</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> element = (</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;h1&gt;时钟&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;h2&gt;current: &#123;new Date().toLocaleString()&#125;&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    )</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">        element,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"string\">'root'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    );</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">setInterval(tick, <span class=\"number\">1000</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>应用一般只进行一次<code>ReactDOM.render()</code>渲染</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>封装时钟</li>\n<li>函数-&gt;类 / 定义局部状态属性</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Clock</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">React</span>.<span class=\"title\">Component</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(props) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">super</span>(props);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.state = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            date: <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">Date</span>(),</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        setInterval(() =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.tick()</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;, <span class=\"number\">1000</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tick() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 更新date</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.setState(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            date: <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">Date</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;h1&gt;Hi, clock Component state new!&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;h2&gt;current: &#123;this.state.date.toLocaleString()&#125;&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        );</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;Clock /&gt;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    document.getElementById('root')</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>state只能在构造函数初始化 <code>this.state={...}</code></li>\n<li>通过<code>this.setState({...})</code>更新并渲染组件</li>\n<li>调用<code>setState</code>时， React会将新的state合并到当前的state中</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"组件生命周期\"><a href=\"#组件生命周期\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件生命周期\"></a>组件生命周期</h2><p><img src=\"https://poplartang.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/FrontEnd/React%E4%B8%AD%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F.png\" alt=\"React中组件的生命周期\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在componentDidMount初始化任务</p>\n<p>在componentWillUnmount清理任务</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"事件处理\"><a href=\"#事件处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"事件处理\"></a>事件处理</h2><h3 id=\"函数定义组件\"><a href=\"#函数定义组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数定义组件\"></a>函数定义组件</h3><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">ActionButton</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">handleClick</span>(<span class=\"params\">e</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">'The Button was clicked.'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;button onClick=&#123;handleClick&#125;&gt;按我&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    );</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"类定义组件\"><a href=\"#类定义组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"类定义组件\"></a>类定义组件</h3><ul>\n<li>注意以下两种写法的区别</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">App</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">React</span>.<span class=\"title\">Component</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    handleClick(e)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">\"handleClick!\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &lt;button onClick=&#123;this.handleClick&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        按钮1 &#123;'&#123;this.handleClick&#125;'&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &lt;/button&gt;\t\t\t\t   </span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &lt;button onClick=&#123;() =&gt; this.handleClick()&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        按钮2 箭头函数 &#123;\"&#123;() =&gt; this.handleClick()&#125;\"&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;/div&gt;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        );</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>默认语法：类的方法默认不会绑定 this，也就是说在handleClick内部的this为undefined</p>\n<p>箭头式语法：在每次App渲染时都会创建一个新的回调函数，可能会造成子组件的额外渲染</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>默认语法this问题解决方案：事件绑定 / 属性初始化器语法：</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><p>在<strong>构造函数绑定</strong>this</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(props) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">super</span>(props);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.handleClick = <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.handleClick.bind(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>使用 <strong>属性初始化器</strong> 语法 声明handleClick</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">handleClick = () =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.setState(preState =&gt; (&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        count: preState.count + <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;))</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>计数器游戏</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项：\"><a href=\"#注意事项：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意事项：\"></a>注意事项：</h2><ul>\n<li><p>组件名首字母必须大写</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>组件的返回值只能有一个根元素</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>props属性是只读的</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","excerpt":"介绍React开发环境的初始化，主要包括：组件定义、props属性、state状态、组件生命周期、事件处理","categories":[{"name":"技术开发","slug":"技术开发","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/技术开发/"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/前端/"},{"name":"React","slug":"React","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/React/"}]},{"title":"关于神是否存在的思考","date":"2017-06-08T01:27:48.000Z","path":"2017/06/关于神的存在/","content":"<p>面对未知, 人们总会善于做出归纳总结, 也许这样会带来安全感。未知的东西也许如薛定谔的猫一样，在盒子未打开之前，猫如同真相一样是处于生和死的叠加态的。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"你说神不存在\"><a href=\"#你说神不存在\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"你说神不存在?\"></a>你说神不存在?</h2><p>最常用的反驳类似于</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一个全能的个体能够创造一块连他自己都搬不动的石头吗？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>但也许对话会是这样的:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">我：你能创造出一块你举不起来的石头吗？</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：能啊，我这就造一个</span><br><span class=\"line\">（石头凭空出现）</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：这就是我举不起来的石头</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：你能把这块你举不起来的石头举起来吗？</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：能啊，你看我给你举一个</span><br><span class=\"line\">（举起来了）</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：你不是说你举不起来吗？！</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：我确实举不起来</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：可是你举起来了！</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：是的，我可以随我的主观意愿做到或做不到所有事情</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：什么TM是的，这在逻辑上根本就说不通！！！</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：用不着说通，逻辑也是我创造的</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"你说神存在\"><a href=\"#你说神存在\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"你说神存在?\"></a>你说神存在?</h2><p>如果神希望大家都信奉、臣服、敬畏祂。那只需要简单的彰显一下自己的与众不同即可。神为何只创造并观察这个世界，不去做任何干扰？比如明目张胆的显示神迹</p>\n<p>如果祂的存在是唯一的，祂为什么默许人类在世间对其进行各种胡编乱造</p>\n<p>如果神的慈爱的，纵观历史长河，何来天地不仁以万物为刍狗</p>\n<h2 id=\"叠加态\"><a href=\"#叠加态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"叠加态\"></a>叠加态</h2><p>这个世界的魅力之一在于一些终极问题在长的时间维度上没有定论，人们在不断从各种角度试探、攻克才精雕细琢出世界的<strong>真相</strong>。</p>\n","excerpt":"面对未知, 人们总会善于做出归纳总结, 也许这样会带来安全感。未知的东西也许如薛定谔的猫一样，在盒子未打开之前，猫如同真相一样是处于生和死的叠加态的。","categories":[{"name":"所思所想","slug":"所思所想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/所思所想/"}],"tags":[{"name":"瞎想","slug":"瞎想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/瞎想/"}]}]